SELECT [t].[ID], [t].[CreatedBy], [t].[CreatedOnDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[LastModifiedBy], [t].[LastModifiedOnDate], [t].[Name], [t].[RowVer], [p].[Id], [p].[CompanyId], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedOnDate], [p].[DOB], [p].[FirstName], [p].[GENDER], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[LastModifiedBy], [p].[LastModifiedOnDate], [p].[LastName], [p].[MiddleName], [p].[RowVer], [p].[Type]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[ID], [c].[CreatedBy], [c].[CreatedOnDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[LastModifiedBy], [c].[LastModifiedOnDate], [c].[Name], [c].[RowVer]
    FROM [Company] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[ID] = @__companyId_0
) AS [t]

     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]
         WHERE [ep].[major_id] = [o].[object_id]
             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0
             AND [ep].[class] = 1
             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )
)
SELECT 1 ELSE SELECT 0
